common problem 
1. What are the functions of PF230? Telescope, measuring distance, golf trajectory compensation, flagpole locking mode, measuring speed and other functions. Please refer to the manual for specific usage. 
2. How to adjust the eyepiece when you can't see clearly through the eyepiece? The magnification of the telescope is 6 times. When you can't see the object clearly in the eyepiece, you can adjust the magnification in clockwise direction, and decrease it in the counterclockwise direction. When the object in the distance is magnified by the eyepiece, the eyepiece number will be blurred, which is a normal phenomenon. After the target is determined, the distance can be clearly seen by adjusting the eyepiece. 
3. Can indoor measurement be carried out? The measurement should be carried out outdoors in a well lit environment; it can also be measured indoors, but the shortest measurement distance should be more than 5 meters, and the light should be bright. 
4. Why does the product have no laser spot? Telescope rangefinder also has laser, but it belongs to invisible laser. In general measurement environment, laser can not be seen, except in specific instrument environment.
